&lt;li&gt;Lead the technical strategy, architecture, and future evolution of the portfolio, guiding the design and modernization of enterprise cloud, DevSecOps, platform, AI/ML, and Zero Trust capabilities that support complex mission environments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Product Management, Technical Leads, and government stakeholders to shape roadmaps, drive architectural decisions, mentor engineering leaders, and ensure delivery of scalable, resilient, and operationally effective solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted technical partner to customer leadership, helping identify innovation opportunities, improve platform health and reliability, and position the program for long-term strategic growth and mission impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct internal engineering excellence by driving delivery innovation and optimizing operational workflows to ensure high-quality, scalable performance across the portfolio.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Systematically identify technical bottlenecks and architect scalable solutions that enable end-users to achieve mission objectives with increased efficiency and cost-effectiveness.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the program’s three areas of responsibility and their Technical Leads in translating complex requirements into phased architectural milestones, ensuring technical deliverables are strategically interleaved throughout the development roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
