&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The candidate&#39;s professional background and relevant work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The specific responsibilities of the role and organization

&lt;p&gt;As &lt;strong&gt;DevSecOps Engineer (Salesforce)&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll support a Salesforce-centered modernization and digital transformation program. This role will enable secure, scalable, and high-performing application delivery for AI-driven development teams focused on rapidly delivering mission-critical capabilities through Salesforce and cloud-native technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
