&lt;p&gt;If you think you can see yourself delivering our mission and pursuing our goals with us, then check out the job description below!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and maintain secure CI/CD pipelines supporting Salesforce application development, configuration, integration, and deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and optimize DevSecOps processes that enable rapid, reliable, and secure delivery across Salesforce environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement automated testing, code quality validation, security scanning, release automation, and deployment orchestration throughout the software development lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Salesforce DevOps tooling and deployment frameworks, including Git-based source control, version management, package deployment, branching strategies, and environment promotion processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate security controls, compliance requirements, and automated vulnerability management into development and deployment workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and manage Infrastructure as Code (IaC), configuration management, and automated provisioning processes across development, test, and production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Salesforce platform security, identity and access management (IAM), role-based access controls, authentication mechanisms, and Zero Trust initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Salesforce developers, architects, product managers, and Scrum Masters to improve development velocity, deployment reliability, and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor platform health, deployment performance, system availability, and security posture while proactively identifying and resolving issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Authority to Operate (ATO) activities, compliance documentation, audit readiness efforts, and continuous monitoring requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate and implement AI-enabled DevSecOps capabilities that improve developer productivity, automate operational tasks, enhance security monitoring, and accelerate software delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive continuous improvement initiatives focused on automation, reliability engineering, operational excellence, and modernization best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain DevSecOps standards, deployment governance, and release management processes across the program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
